ygData.messageBody:
OOPS! Just as I was headin out to do some actual
work, I realized I'd made an error! The Chessboard is
in NorthEAST Butcherblock, not Northwest! To get
there, follow the road til you reach the zone area to
Greater Feydark, then turn north. Can't miss it.<br>
Also, I have a question as yet unanswered. I looted an
item off the Undead King at Chessboard. It's a 'Rune
of Nefagen'. If any of you could tell me what is/is
used for/worth, I'd really appreciate it.<br><br>
Foleen
